---
name: data_csv
description: Process CSV and TSV by field name with Miller (mlr) — select columns, filter rows, sort, and convert to JSON, correctly handling quoted fields and embedded commas that break cut and awk. Use to extract a CSV column by header, filter records, or turn a CSV into JSON.
kind: tool
tags: [data, csv, miller, mlr, tsv, records]
use_when: [cut a column from a csv by name, filter csv rows, convert csv to json, handle quoted csv fields, sort a csv, process tsv, csv without breaking on commas]
